title: DJ Square - Complete-258 Tracks
description:
Not uploaded here by the artist himself, but I dont think he would mind. Anyways, most, if not all tracks are UK Hardcore or Bouncy Techno styled

Since K-Trax Digital and most other indie labels have been removed from IMODownload, These tracks can't be found anywhere. Can't imagine me putting them back up for sale, so here you are. Enjoy!

Unmixed, Full Length, Absolutely Free.
See Below For Tracklist. Also, a small comment would be nice :)

258 Tracks
15 Discs
1.84GB
VBR mp3

CD13: The Long Lost Files
A collection of tracks that have been missing for the last 6 years. After a quick garage clearout, I found an unlabelled disc with them all on it. Most of which have never been heard by anyone other than me.
CD14: Shine DJs Collection
CD15: From The Vaults
72 tracks featuring unheard early samples, alternative takes, vocals and incomplete tracks. This disc may not appeal to alot of people, but didn't feel it was a 'Complete' collection without it.
